<p class="">I can assure the hon. Member for South Kensington (Sir W. Davison) that the majority of Members on this side of the House do not receive a halfpenny from a trade union, a cooperative society or any outside organisation.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
