        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-82ff8cef-e345-494a-8cf8-b333881d25f1">
                Sir W. Davison
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-82ff8cef-e345-494a-8cf8-b333881d25f1" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1937-06-22/debates/e8f7ec0b-e4b3-4a90-9812-6b1a8306ef86/PaymentOfMembers#contribution-82ff8cef-e345-494a-8cf8-b333881d25f1">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">My point was not that there was any comparison between the cost of this increase and the cost of armaments, but that the community was being asked to make serious sacrifices in order to provide this immense sum of£1,500,000,000.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-82ff8cef-e345-494a-8cf8-b333881d25f1" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1937-06-22/debates/e8f7ec0b-e4b3-4a90-9812-6b1a8306ef86/PaymentOfMembers#contribution-82ff8cef-e345-494a-8cf8-b333881d25f1">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
