<div class="content-item" id="contribution-650a94f5-1af7-4c4f-a6f6-30cde08ef808">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-650a94f5-1af7-4c4f-a6f6-30cde08ef808">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
